 | quote  = "He beat out, [[Charlie Sheen]] in ''[[Two and a Half Men]]'', the nighttime soap ''[[Grey’s Anatomy]]'',  ''[[Heroes (TV series)|Heroes]]'', and the closest to edging him out was ''[[Lost (TV series)|Lost]]''… but it lost. The man with the cane was intriguing to me. So, I decided to give House, M.D. a try."
